text: Nolan North (born October 31, 1970) is an American voice actor known for voicing Nathan Drake from the Uncharted franchise. ==Filmography== * Crash of the Titans (2007) * Crash: Mind over Mutant (2008) * Portal 2 (2011) * Batman: Arkham City (2011) * Batman: Arkham Origins (2013) * Batman: Arkham Knight (2015) * Uncharted 4: A Thief's End (2016) ==Other websites== * * Nolan North at Behind The Voice Actors Category:1970 births Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American video game actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from New Haven, Connecticut Category:Living people
